OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777536371
OL,3,CBank of England expected to hold
OL,4,Cinterest rates steady despite
OL,5,Cinflation rise
OL,7,FThe Bank of England's decision will
OL,8,Fcome a day after the US Federal
OL,9,FReserve announces its own monetary
OL,10,Fpolicy, with economists also expecting
OL,11,Frates to be kept on hold while
OL,12,Funcertainty about the economic effects
OL,13,Fof the conflict persists.
OL,15,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,16,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,17,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,18,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
